  "intent_precise": "NGS Prep Part 2/3: Library Quantification: Using 2ml reagent rack (tuberack, slot 2), qpcr_plate (plate, slot 4), DNA plate (plate, slot 5), elution plate (plate, slot 9). With magnetic module, temperature module. (1) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (2) Transfer 18\u00b5L from water 0 to destination A1. (3) Mix 3 times at 9\u00b5L. (4) Transfer 10\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (5) Mix 5 times at 90\u00b5L. (6) Pause: Replace 10 \u00b5L tip rack and insert QPCR mastermix into position B1 of reagent rack. (7) Transfer 4\u00b5L from source (A1, A1) to destination (A1, A1).",
